Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\"}, {\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Porte de la Chapelle\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythmic gymnastics\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"so-called \\\"crack hill\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"a meeting place\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 300 addicts\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since becoming a symbol of the capital's drugs problems, police have stepped up patrols, while the hill has been relandscaped and planted with trees, disbursing the dealers and their customers.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a symbol\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's drugs problems\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"patrols\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the hill\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"trees\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the dealers\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"their customers\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the last two months, we have got far fewer addicts in the area because they have moved on,\\\" the head of local residents' association Vivre au 93 La Chapelle, Jean-Michel Metayer, told AFP.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999980903103323, \"rank\": 1.9096753110999126e-06, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last two months\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"far fewer addicts\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents' association Vivre\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"93 La Chapelle, Jean-Michel Metayer\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Migrant camps that were also a constant feature under the raised sections of the nearby ringroad and A1 motorway have also been prevented from forming, under tactics decried by some charities.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Migrant camps\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"a constant feature\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the raised sections\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearby ringroad\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"tactics\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"some charities\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all hope that the work changes the reputation of the area, which is not very good,\\\" added Metayer.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the reputation\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"Metayer\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo, who launched her re-election bid from Porte de la Chapelle in 2020, has made the new arena a core part of a 500-million-euro (S$726.13 million) makeover of the district.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"-election bid\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"la\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the new arena\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"a 500-million-euro (S$726.13 million) makeover\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"the district\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other regeneration efforts include tearing up the main thoroughfare, which serves as a major route into central Paris.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.029172153706331e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other regeneration efforts\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the main thoroughfare\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a major route\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The space for cars has been dramatically reduced, while granite-edged cycle lanes, footpaths and hundreds of trees have been added, reflecting the eco-minded political priorities of Hidalgo's 10 years in power.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9998788548622973, \"rank\": 0.00012115981571963874, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The space\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"granite-edged cycle lanes\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"footpaths\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"trees\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"the eco-minded political priorities\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People used to talk about this area as a 'no-go zone',\\\" Hidalgo told reporters on Sunday as she inaugurated the arena, adding that she found the description \\\"unfair on local residents.\\\"\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"this area\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'no-go zone\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"Hidalgo\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"the description\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But we made a commitment to change things.\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a commitment\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today we have the demonstration that change is possible,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the demonstration\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The arena - owned by the city of Paris and branded as the Adidas Arena - will become the home of the ambitious US-owned Paris Basketball club, which will play its first game there on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.029172153706331e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 2722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Basketball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"the Adidas Arena\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"its first game\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In late 2025, a university research site, Campus Condorcet, will also open nearby for up to 4,500 people daily.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Condorcet\", \"score\": 0.9992716146971271, \"rank\": 0.0004763178084175648, \"text\": \"Condorcet\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Condorcet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Condorcet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a university research site\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 4,500 people\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Between the campus and the arena, we have two major components which are going to reconfigure and transform the area,\\\" said Nicolas Dupeux, director general of the arena's operating company, Paris Entertainment Company, told AFP.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Dupeux\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dupeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Dupeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Dupeux\"}, {\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.029172153706331e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3117, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999980903103323, \"rank\": 1.9096753110999126e-06, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the campus\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"two major components\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3008}, {\"ngram\": \"director general\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena's operating company\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With sport, music and restaurants, we expect 1.2-1.3 million people to come here per year.\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"1.2-1.3 million people\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's massive,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This influx is going to create a dynamic in the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This influx\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"a dynamic\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers of the 2024 Paris Olympics and Paralympics, which run from July 26 to September 8, are keen to present their Games as a new low-budget model, with almost all the sports set to take place in pre-existing or temporary infrastructure.\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3336}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3373}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"their Games\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"a new low-budget model\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"almost all the sports\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3496}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-existing or temporary infrastructure\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new aquatics centre has also been built from scratch, a few kilometres (miles) away on the other side of the ringroad.\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A new aquatics centre\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"a few kilometres\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"miles\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3646}, {\"ngram\": \"the ringroad\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other facilities, including the national Stade de France stadium, are being upgraded, while events such as skateboarding, beach volleyball or archery are set to take place in ephemeral venues scattered around the city.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3706, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other facilities\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"ephemeral venues\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3856}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Helping regenerate the Porte de la Chapelle area, as well as the nearby Saint-Ouen and Saint-Denis suburbs where other Olympics investments have been concentrated, is seen as one of the most promising legacy achievements of the Games.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3908, \"end\": 3928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Porte de la Chapelle\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_C